Privacy Policy of Sopa de Letras (android app)

We do not collect or store any of your Personal Data. It's a simple game.

The rights of Users
Users have the right, at any time, to know whether their Personal Data has been stored and can consult this privacy policy.

This Application does not support “Do Not Track” requests.
To determine whether any of the third party services it uses honor the “Do Not Track” requests, please read their privacy policies.

Changes to this privacy policy
Cristian Cortez reserves the right to make changes to this privacy policy at any time by giving notice to its Users on this page. 
It is strongly recommended to check this page often, referring to the date of the last modification listed at the bottom. 
If a User objects to any of the changes to the Policy, the User must cease using this Application and can request that Cristian Cortez removes the Personal Data. 
Unless stated otherwise, the then-current privacy policy applies to all Personal Data Cristian Cortez has about Users.



